--- .gitignore (原始)


+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Compiled Python files
*.pyc
__pycache__/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage reports
.coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```